{"title":"声声慢　周恩来遗物陈列馆","authors":["顾浩"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":2,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声慢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来遗物陈列馆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾浩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是在淮安？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是京城？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到此怎生辨识！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因有万缕情思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精纺细织。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雕栏画栋庭院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一股清流润巨石。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陋室里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理万机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽是粗衣淡食。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见件件遗物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人何去？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"念之满襟泪湿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千古风范，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英姿永不消失！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今红日高照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神州地，青松挺直。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月圆了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟人含笑飞花拾。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}